Package: ciwidth
Title: Sample size calculations based on confidence intervals
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Stefan Nygaard", "Hansen", , "stefanh@ph.au.dk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0877-556X"))
Description: The package enables calculation of the required sample size to ensure that  confidence intervals for a mean or mean difference are within a certain width with a certain probability.
